PersonalBiography
&nbsp;
GuandingYu(S'05-M'07-SM'13)receivedtheB.E.degreeandthePh.D.degreefromZhejiangUniversityin2001and2006,respectively,bothinCommunicationEngineering.Afterthat,hejoinedZhejiangUniversity,whereheisanAssociatedProfessorintheDepartmentofInformationandElectronicEngineering.SinceJuly2013,hehasbeenavisitingprofessorintheSchoolofElectricalandComputerEngineering,GeorgiaInstituteofTechnology,Atlanta,GA,USA.&nbsp;<spanstyle="font-size:14.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:
&quot;TimesNewRoman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;">
Dr.Yuservedasareviewerformanyjournalsandconferences,suchasIEEEJSAC,TCOM,TWC,TVT,IJCS,ICC,VTC,Globecom,WCNC,etc.Hehasservedasthegeneralco-chairofCRNet2010workshop,TPCco-chairforGreenCommunications&amp;ComputingsymposiumofChinacom2013andTPCmemberforvariousacademicconferences.HeisaguesteditorofIEEECommunicationsMagazinespecialissueonfull-duplexcommunicationsandaneditorofIEEEJournalonSelectedAreasinCommunications-SeriesonGreenCommunicationsandNetworking.Hisresearchinterestincludesenergy-efficientwirelesscommunicationsystemdesign,device-to-devicecommunications,andsmallcelltechnique.<spanstyle="font-size:14.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:
